questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The pattern followed here is shown below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From row 1:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(63, 49, ?)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 7&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 9 = 63, 7&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 7 = 49, 7&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11 = 77&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From row 2:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(99, 77, 121)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 11&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 9 = 99, 11&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 7 = 77, 11&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11 = 121&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From row 3:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(135, 105, 165)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 9 = 135, 15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 7 = 105, 15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11 = 165&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;77&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসৃত ধাঁচটি&nbsp;নীচে দেখানো হয়েছে:</p>

<p>সারি 1 থেকে:</p>

<p><strong>(63, 49, ?) &rarr; 7 &times; 9 = 63, 7 &times; 7 = 49, 7 &times; 11 = 77</strong></p>

<p>সারি 2 থেকে:</p>

<p>(99, 77, 121) &rarr; 11 &times; 9 = 99, 11 &times; 7 = 77, 11 &times; 11 = 121</p>

<p>সারি 3 থেকে:</p>

<p>(135, 105, 165) &rarr; 15 &times; 9 = 135, 15 &times; 7 = 105, 15 &times; 11 = 165</p>

<p>অতএব, "<strong>77</strong>" সঠিক উত্তর।</p>

